model.name: Anand2003 - Reactions of the Intrinsic Pathway of Blood Coagulation with Platelet Activation

body.p: Inhomogeneous blood coagulation model. Encoded model contains reactions of the intrinsic pathway with platelet activation. Initial conditions provided. Mostly an extension of Zarnitsina1996.
